2019-07-16  Tobias Junghans <tobydox@veyon.io>

	* libvncclient/rfbproto.c: rfbproto: invert bitmask using bitwise
	NOT Inverting a bitmask should be done using a bitwise NOT instead of a
	logical NOT.

