	endianness detection, but introduced a typo and problems for Windows
	builds (no endian.h, different definition of
	LIBVNCSERVER_WORDS_BIGENDIAN).  Fix both issues.  Signed-off-by: Stefan Weil <sw@weilnetz.de>

