2008-02-01  runge <runge>

	* x11vnc/ChangeLog, x11vnc/README, x11vnc/connections.c,
	x11vnc/help.c, x11vnc/misc/enhanced_tightvnc_viewer/README,
	x11vnc/misc/enhanced_tightvnc_viewer/bin/util/ss_vncviewer,
